data.description: Welcome to this Charming  Home in Beautiful Heber Valley! Featuring six generously sized bedrooms, this property offers flexible living options for families and working professionals. The newly updated kitchen boasts quartz counters and new cabinetry throughout, perfect for preparing meals or hosting gatherings. The garage has been thoughtfully re-done with insulation, finished walls, and coated flooring, providing a functional space for vehicles or hobbies. The large storage area underneath the home offers plenty of additional storage space. Outside, you'll appreciate the ample concrete parking area for RVs and boats. Nestled in a sought-after location in Heber Valley, this well-maintained property is sure to impress. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
